cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new deep learning architecture, which involves end-to-end training and metric learning, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of class memory module and score weighting method, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography (cs.CR), respectively.
